      "body" : "@sipa It is CAutoFile being modified.  That is \"RAII wrapper for FILE*\" and is used outside the network wire protocol and core serialization of data structures.  Both [1] and [2] want to read text files, and using an RAII wrapper for FILE* is the logical choice.\r\n\r\n[1] https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/src/bitcoin-tx.cpp#L126\r\n[2] https://github.com/jgarzik/bitcoin/blob/2014_ext_services/src/extservices.cpp\r\n",
